OL,10,     GJessica and her friend Haskell
OL,11,     GDrake unravel the mysterious
OL,12,     Gdeath of a corrupt newspaper
OL,13,     Gmogul.
OL,14,G1400FMurder She Wrote
OL,15,     GJessica spends her vacation
OL,16,     Gproving that fellow crime-buster
OL,17,     GThomas Magnum is innocent of two
OL,18,     Gmurders.
