OL,4,G2100FWWII Battles in Colour
OL,5,     GJuly 1943. The German advance has
OL,6,     Gstalled, but Hitler is convinced
OL,7,     Ghis new generation of tanks will
OL,8,     Gput the Reich back on the path to
OL,9,     Gdomination. His target: the
OL,10,     GSoviet town of Kursk.
OL,11,G2200FWWII Battles in Colour
OL,12,     GIn late 1944, Allied confidence
OL,13,     Gwas high. But the war was about
OL,14,     Gto take a dramatic turn,
OL,15,     Gresulting in the U.S. army's
OL,16,     Glargest and bloodiest conflict of
OL,17,     GWWII: The Battle of the Bulge.
